{"tid":2444722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「人民有顛覆暴政的自由」","createTime":"2021-03-13T04:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T12:29:08.000Z","uid":147376,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6a8aa0f58ef90bb675f93ab56749a9899bb54c95","tid":2444722,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:54:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10159954023652448/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10159954023652448%2F&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=aa9c13f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10159954023652448/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMbofsQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMbofsQ.jpg&h=ae230f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名示威伯伯中午約12時手持基本法及寫上「人民有顛覆暴政的自由」的白色紙板，在高等法院外高聲抗議「違反基本法」，隨即被警員開咪警告他放下紙牌及出示身份證。<br />\n<br />\n伯伯起初未有理會繼續抗議，開咪的男警一度向他指「你塊牌就快打到我」，女警則要求他「戴好口罩先講」。男警指伯伯的行為「有機會對警察構成危險」，隨即有約10名警員上前增援。伯伯被指在公眾地方行為不檢，他在警員要求時一邊出示身份證仍不忘手持基本法理論。"},{"pid":"b4334bfa1acb3c4f0e8c48cb3c600fbc0f2dae28","tid":2444722,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61878bf6a1c7aa7a8ed231e5b3ddca7a3f3849ac","tid":2444722,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421ebdea37970301fc54b9a6ab6b9edb43ced6df","tid":2444722,"uid":147376,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:56:40.000Z","msg